examples.en: The Russians exported Marxism to Africa.

examples.en: We should consider this problem from the viewpoint of the Russians.

examples.en: Far sooner than anyone thought possible, the Russians exploded an atomic bomb.

examples.en: According to the Secretary of State, the Russians face no threat from an expanded NATO.
